 game mechanics + gamepad support.<br>    </li><li>Use of physics and changing gravity.<br>    </li><li>Environmental puzzles.<br>    </li><li>One item-based inventory system, hey a button doesn't have pockets, deal with it.<br>    </li><li>Three game difficulties to select from.<br>    </li><li>Lots of steam achievements.</li></ul><br>The wacky premise of Bad Pad is told in songs and is set around a gamepad's buttons who came to life, their endless battles, mind controlling machines and a little bit of time traveling.<br><br>Join Square in his adventures, survive Evil Pen's hellish castles, help save Hexa and Trapezoid and probably the rest of the world!<br><br>Give Bad Pad DEMO a try, it is always up-to-date and if you decide to buy to the full game you can continue playing with your saved progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/517210/extras/ab7f06b31359f0dbb2ab4910eb912508.poster.avif?t=1745970981\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/517210/extras/ab7f06b31359f0dbb2ab4910eb912508.webm?t=1745970981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/517210/extras/ab7f06b31359f0dbb2ab4910eb912508.mp4?t=1745970981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/517210/extras/e908507c67d50fac9e8d9975a5200f63.poster.avif?t=1745970981\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/517210/extras/e908507c67d50fac9e8d9975a5200f63.webm?t=1745970981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/517210/extras/e908507c67d50fac9e8d9975a5200f